<i>Yeah, that's how cops do it.</i>

400
00:23:53,225 --> 00:23:54,518
<i>What was going on here?</i>

401
00:23:54,685 --> 00:23:57,020
I think we need to know
a lot more about that.

402
00:23:57,187 --> 00:24:00,065
That needs to be the subject
of a significant investigation.

403
00:24:00,232 --> 00:24:01,733
What happened? How did it happen?

404
00:24:01,900 --> 00:24:03,485
Why did it happen,
