405
00:24:04,194 --> 00:24:07,990
Try to imagine
what those poor bastards were feeling

406
00:24:08,156 --> 00:24:11,618
when they were jumping
out of that building to their death.

407
00:24:11,785 --> 00:24:15,914
Those... those... those young guys
and cops and firemen that ran

408
