into that building,
never asked a question, and they're dead.

409
00:24:20,169 --> 00:24:22,087
And families' lives are ruined.

410
00:24:22,254 --> 00:24:24,882
And they'll never,
they'll never have peace.

411
00:24:25,591 --> 00:24:27,968
And if I had to inconvenience...

412
00:24:29,678 --> 00:24:33,724
