416
00:24:40,647 --> 00:24:42,357
-No, no, it's just...
-No one would question.

417
00:24:42,524 --> 00:24:45,485
You know, you got a lawyer? Fine.
Counsellor, fine!

418
00:24:45,652 --> 00:24:47,821
Mr. Bin Laden, this is why I'm asking you,

419
00:24:47,988 --> 00:24:49,698
it's not because I think
that you're anything,

420
00:24:49,865 --> 00:24:52,618
I just want to ask you the questions
that I would anybody.

