<i>Lila had called to tell me</i>

2231
01:53:04,826 --> 01:53:08,080
<i>that she was coming down
<i>from Flint to Washington, D.C.</i></i>

2232
01:53:08,247 --> 01:53:10,457
<i>to attend a job's conference.</i>

2233
01:53:11,041 --> 01:53:13,961
<i>On her break, she said
<i>she was going to go and pay a visit</i></i>

2234
01:53:14,127 --> 01:53:15,337
<i>to the White House.</i>

2235
01:53:15,504 --> 01:53:16,421
[helicopters throbbing]

2236
01:53:21,677 --> 01:53:22,719
[Lila sobbing]

2237
01:53:22,886 --> 01:53:25,430
[woman with accent, high-pitched]
Killed! Bush killed children!

2238
01:53:25,597 --> 01:53:28,225
-Iraqi children!
-My son killed.

2239
01:53:28,392 --> 01:53:30,269
He killed my people
in the Spain yesterday.

2240
01:53:30,435 --> 01:53:33,730
-Yes!
-He lies, kill people, your children too.

2241
01:53:33,897 --> 01:53:36,650
-Yes, my son.
-Business to do Iraq now.

2242
01:53:36,817 --> 01:53:38,735
And they killing
all these young Americans.

2243
01:53:38,902 --> 01:53:41,280
-Yes.
-For what? For oil.

2244
01:53:41,446 --> 01:53:43,156
Bush is a terrorist!

2245
01:53:43,323 --> 01:53:45,158
No, he isn't, this is all staged!

2246
01:53:45,325 --> 01:53:47,119
-Yes, he's the butcher of Iraq.
-This is staged.

2247
01:53:47,286 --> 01:53:48,287
My son!

2248
01:53:48,453 --> 01:53:49,580
Where was he killed?

2249
01:53:49,746 --> 01:53:51,790
You tell me my son
is not a stage?

2250
01:53:51,957 --> 01:53:54,585
-Where was he killed?
-He was killed in Karbala.

2251
01:53:54,751 --> 01:53:56,211
[protester rambles on]

2252
01:53:56,378 --> 01:54:00,549
April second, it's not a stage,
my son is dead.

2253
01:54:00,716 --> 01:54:02,968
Well, a lot of other people too.

2254
01:54:03,135 --> 01:54:06,722
[protester continues in background]

2255
01:54:07,389 --> 01:54:08,932
[woman shouts] Blame Al-Qaeda!

2256
01:54:09,099 --> 01:54:12,394
[throbbing]

2257
01:54:13,103 --> 01:54:15,063
[Michael Moore]
What did that woman yell at you?

2258
01:54:15,230 --> 01:54:17,566
That I'm supposed to blame the Al-Qaeda.

2259
01:54:18,567 --> 01:54:22,946
The Al-Qaeda didn't make a decision
to send my son to Iraq.

2260
01:54:23,113 --> 01:54:24,031
[sobs]

2261
01:54:24,198 --> 01:54:26,867
Ignorance that we deal with
with everyday people!

2262
01:54:27,034 --> 01:54:28,869
[nervous laughter]
'Cause they don't know.

2263
01:54:29,036 --> 01:54:30,996
People think they know,
