I thought I knew, but I didn't know.

2265
01:54:33,790 --> 01:54:35,167
[sniffling]

2266
01:54:37,085 --> 01:54:38,587
[sobbing]

2267
01:54:39,421 --> 01:54:41,089
I need my son!

2268
01:54:41,256 --> 01:54:44,885
[crying uncontrollably]

2269
01:54:45,052 --> 01:54:48,055
[machinery beeping]

2270
01:54:48,222 --> 01:54:55,187
[sobbing and sniffling]

2271
01:54:59,775 --> 01:55:03,445
God, it's tougher than I thought
it was gonna be to be here.

2272
01:55:05,155 --> 01:55:08,784
But it's freeing also,
because I finally have a place to...

2273
