[Michael Moore]<i> I guess I was tired of
<i>seeing people like Lila Lipscomb suffer.</i></i>

2279
01:55:24,591 --> 01:55:28,554
<i>Especially when,
<i>out of the 535 members of Congress,</i></i>

2280
